title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I loved this stream so much! Thanks for chatting with us!
The song “I swear” kinda goes along with the pinky swear, pinky truth thing....so funny 😄

If Ally no longer has any fear, then why did she put a knife in her pocket before she answered the door to Kai?  I think when she was laying in Ozzy’s bed with his little train, she thought up the entire scheme to overthrow Kai and get Ozzy back.  She’s not going to be just another car on the track, she’s taking the engine and becoming her own engineer!
description:
Welcome to American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Streams! Streams are every Wednesday @ 9 pm and 9 pm CST. Host is MaryGirl Moody.
